title: Court In Iran Convicts Iranian-American Journalist Jason Rezaian
text:
Published By: Huffington Post Media - Today 
WASHINGTON, Oct 11 (Reuters) - A court in Iran has convicted Iranian-American journalist Jason Rezaian, but details have yet to be disclosed...
